_sText:
This is a simple map i made in the dust 2 style. This map has 24 spawnpoints and is perfect for gg.
This map has a hidden surprise in the center column of the circular building. Break the wall opposite the largest door to get to the unlimited awp spawner inside.

I would appreciate it if someone could put it on the server. Please send me a message if you do so i can play.
  

hope you have fun.
